'''''Men's Vogue''''' was a monthly men's magazine that covered fashion, design, art, culture, sports and technology.  On October 30, 2008 [[Cond<U+00E9> Nast Publications|Cond<U+00E9> Nast]] announced that they intended to fold the magazine into  Vogue proper as a bi-annual subscriber's supplement. However, the magazine has ceased to be published since its original folding date. 

